Questions:
If you choose not to participate in the ACTIVATE study, what alternative option is recommended for increasing your physical activity?
A) Enrolling in a different clinical trial focused on dietary changes; 
B) Consulting with your doctor or healthcare provider to start and maintain an exercise routine; 
C) There are no alternatives provided; 
D) Immediate enrollment in the exercise program without participating in the study.

Correct answer: B

If you experience any harm from participating in the ACTIVATE study, whom should you contact?

A) The Human Subjects Division at the University of Washington;
B) Kerryn Reding, the Principal Investigator of the study;
C) The National Cancer Institute;
D) Your personal healthcare provider.

Correct answer: B) Kerryn Reding, the Principal Investigator of the study.
